SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR SOLUTION $PAR
By solving the system
\[ \eqalign{6x_1 -2x_2 - x_3 =0  {\rm\ Carbon\ atoms}\] 
\[12x_1 - 6x_2 = 0  {\rm\ Hydrogen\ atoms} \] \[6x_1 -x_2 -2x_3 =0 {\rm \ Oxygen\ atoms\]
we get the general solution
\[x_1 = s,\ x_2 = 2s, \ x_3 = 2s \]
